{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-cours-md-js","path":"/1g/nsi/5-interactions-entre-lhomme-et-la-machine-sur-le-web/2-ecriture-dune-page-html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<details class=\"programme\"><summary>Programme Officiel</summary><div><table class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\"><thead class=\"table-warning\"><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Contenus</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Capacités attendues</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Commentaires</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Modalités de l'interaction\nentre l'homme et la\nmachine</p><p>Événements</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Identifier les différents\ncomposants graphiques\npermettant d'interagir avec une\napplication Web</p><p>Identifier les événements que\nles fonctions associées aux\ndifférents composants\ngraphiques sont capables de\ntraiter</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Il s’agit d’examiner le code HTML\nd’une page comprenant des\ncomposants graphiques et de\ndistinguer ce qui relève de la\ndescription des composants\ngraphiques en HTML de leur\ncomportement (réaction aux\névénements) programmé par\nexemple en JavaScript.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><a class=\"lien-programme\" href=\"../programme/\">Lien vers le programme complet</a></details>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Dans ce chapitre nous allons approfondir nos connaissances sur le langage <code class=\"language-text\">html</code> déjà étudié en\nseconde. Pour rappel, le W3C a défini deux langages afin de bien séparer <em>le fond et la forme</em>. Le\n<code class=\"language-text\">html</code> vu dans ce chapitre décrit le contenu du document: le <em>fond</em>, et le <code class=\"language-text\">css</code> que l'on étudiera\ndans le prochain chapitre décrit sa <em>forme</em>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a title=\"W3C [CC-BY-3.0 (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0)], via Wikimedia Commons\" href=\"http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File%3AHTML5_logo_and_wordmark.svg\"><img class=\"right\" width=\"256\" alt=\"HTML5 logo and wordmark\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/HTML5_logo_and_wordmark.svg/256px-HTML5_logo_and_wordmark.svg.png\"/></a></p>\n<p>C'est un langage qui utilise des balises entre chevrons(<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;balise&gt;</code>) pour structurer les pages web\net leur donner un sens.</p>\n<p>Une page <code class=\"language-text\">html</code> commence toujours par indiquer le <code class=\"language-text\">doctype</code>. Depuis html5 c'est très simple:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token name\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><em>C'est quand même mieux que son ancêtre en html4:</em></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">HTML</span> <span class=\"token name\">PUBLIC</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>Le document est séparé en deux grandes parties:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>le <code class=\"language-text\">head</code>: qui contient des informations utiles au navigateur et aux robots qui consultent votre\npage.</li>\n<li>le <code class=\"language-text\">body</code>: qui contient les informations qui seront effectivement affichées à l’écran.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"structure-modèle\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#structure-mod%C3%A8le\" aria-label=\"structure modèle permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Structure modèle</h2>\n<p>Voici une structure qui peut vous servir quand vous commencez une nouvelle page web.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token name\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Un document minuscule<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Titre principal de mon document<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Ceci est un commentaire --></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      Regarde maman, je suis en train de coder en\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>abbr</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Hyper Text Markup Language<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>en<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>HTML<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> !\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"les-principales-balises\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#les-principales-balises\" aria-label=\"les principales balises permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Les principales balises</h2>\n<p>Le langage <code class=\"language-text\">html</code> utilise des balises pour indiquer le sens sémantique des éléments d'une page. Ces\nbalises ou tags permettent de construire une hiérarchie au sein du document appelée DOM(Document\nObject Model).</p>\n<p>Toutes les balises sont référencées sur le site\n<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element\">MDN</a>, en voici quelques-unes.</p>\n<div><table class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\"><thead class=\"table-warning\"><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>balise</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>rôle</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>exemple</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;h1&gt;</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;h2&gt;</code>, ...<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;h6&gt;</code></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Titres et sous-titres</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;h1&gt;Titre principal de mon document&lt;/h1&gt;</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;p&gt;</code></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Paragraphe</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;p&gt;Comme je descendais des Fleuves impassibles.&lt;/p&gt;</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;strong&gt;</code></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>texte important(en gras par défaut)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;p&gt;Comme je &lt;strong&gt;descendais&lt;/strong&gt; des Fleuves impassibles.&lt;/p&gt;</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;em&gt;</code></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>texte en emphase(en italiques par défaut)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;p&gt;Comme je &lt;em&gt;descendais&lt;/em&gt; des Fleuves impassibles.&lt;/p&gt;</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;a href=&quot;dest&quot;&gt;</code></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Lien vers la page d'URL <code class=\"language-text\">dest</code></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wikipedia.fr/&quot;&gt;Se rendre sur Wikipedia&lt;/a&gt;</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img src=&quot;image.png&quot;/&gt;</code></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Affichage de l'image d'URI <code class=\"language-text\">image.png</code></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img src=&quot;photo.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Photo de mon chat&quot;/&gt;</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;ul&gt;</code></p><p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;li&gt;</code></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>liste à puce</p><p>élément d'une liste</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>1er élément de la liste<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>2e élément de la liste<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>3e ...<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<details class=\"plus\" data-titre=\"Balises orphelines\"><summary>Balises orphelines</summary><p>Certaines balises ne contiennent pas de texte, elles n'ont donc pas de balises fermantes.</p><p>On les appelle des balises <em>orphelines</em>. Elles ont une syntaxe particulière: <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;balise/&gt;</code>.</p><p>Par exemple la balise d'image <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img /&gt;</code>.\n<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img src=&quot;logo.png&quot; alt=&quot;Logo du site&quot; /&gt;</code></p></details>\n<details class=\"plus\" data-titre=\"Attributs d&#x27;une balise\"><summary>Attributs d'une balise</summary><p>Les attributs d'un élément, permettent de modifier son comportement ou de fournir des métadonnées.</p><p>Par exemple, la balise <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img /&gt;</code> possède deux attributs obligatoires:</p><ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">src</code> pour préciser l'adresse de l'image à afficher</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">alt</code> pour expliquer le contenu de l'image si l'image ne s'affiche pas ou pour décrire l'image\naux personnes non-voyantes.</li>\n</ul></details>\n<div class=\"prop\"><p>Seul le texte écrit entre les balises ouvrante et fermantes s'affiche à l'écran.</p></div>\n<h2 id=\"règles-décriture\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#r%C3%A8gles-d%C3%A9criture\" aria-label=\"règles décriture permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Règles d'écriture</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Les balises ouvrantes et fermantes doivent toujours être correctement imbriquées, c'est à dire\nque les balises fermantes doivent êtres écrites dans l'ordre inverse des balises d'ouverture. Une\nbonne imbrication des balises est une des règles à respecter afin d'avoir un code valide. <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/fr/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Introduction#Les_balises\">Source\nMDN</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Voici un exemple de code valide :</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ceci est <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>strong</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>très<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>strong</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> important<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>.</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>Voici un exemple de code non-valide :</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ceci est <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>strong</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>très<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> important<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>strong</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>.</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"quelques-petits-plus\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#quelques-petits-plus\" aria-label=\"quelques petits plus permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Quelques petits plus</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Les commentaires sont écrits <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;!-- Ceci est un commentaire --&gt;</code></li>\n<li>On écrit en général les balises en minuscules.</li>\n<li>L'indentation n'est pas obligatoire, mais elle rend le fichier plus lisible.</li>\n<li>Les balises <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;div&gt;</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;header&gt;</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;article&gt;</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;footer&gt;</code> ont été créé dans la version 5 de <code class=\"language-text\">html</code>\nafin de créer des blocs spécifiques dans la page.</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#structure-mod%C3%A8le\">Structure modèle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#les-principales-balises\">Les principales balises</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#r%C3%A8gles-d%C3%A9criture\">Règles d'écriture</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#quelques-petits-plus\">Quelques petits plus</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"tags":["html","balises","attributs"]},"fields":{"classe":"1g","chapter":"Ecriture d'une page HTML","matter":"nsi","nChapter":"2","part":"Interactions entre l'homme et la machine sur le Web","nPart":"5"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"1g/nsi/5-interactions-entre-lhomme-et-la-machine-sur-le-web/2-ecriture-dune-page-html","chapter":"Ecriture d'une page HTML"}},"staticQueryHashes":["604483588"]}